{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7d1fbf4a63","title":"关于边防军务必在九月底以前完成一切作战准备致高岗电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"97a86db8d1","index":0,"year":1950,"month":8,"day":18,"articleId":"7d1fbf4a63"}],"tags":[{"id":"af71a4eedb","name":"高岗","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"efdaa7d915","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7d1fbf4a63","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"高岗，当时任中国人民解放军东北军区司令员兼政治委员。"},{"id":"5789b162c4","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7d1fbf4a63","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"肖劲光，当时任中国人民解放军海军司令员，1950年7月被任命兼东北边防军副司令员，后来东北边防军司令部没有正式成立。"}],"contents":[{"id":"19c3d6c877","type":"title","text":"关于边防军务必在九月底以前完成一切作战准备致高岗“电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7d1fbf4a63"},{"id":"efdaa7d915","type":"paragraph","text":"高岗同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7d1fbf4a63"},{"id":"5789b162c4","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）八月十五日送来你在边防军干部会议的报告收到了，这个报告是正确的。（二）肖劲光同志来告有关边防军的各项问题，这些问题都可以解决。（三）边防军完成训练及其他准备工作的时间可延长至九月底，请你加紧督促，务在九月册日以前完成一切准备","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7d1fbf4a63"},{"id":"8d490eb78d","type":"subtitle","text":"工作。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7d1fbf4a63"},{"id":"583a2cc2e0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7d1fbf4a63"},{"id":"29f38756d5","type":"paragraph","text":"八月十八日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7d1fbf4a63"}],"page":{"id":"51d6d49683","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7d1fbf4a63","start":87,"end":87}}}},"__N